sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Platform Gateway<br/>(Istio Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant ExtProc as Payload Processing<br/>(ext_proc)<br/>9004/TCP gRPC
    participant MPR as model-provider-resolver<br/>(in-process plugin)
    participant APITrans as api-translation<br/>(in-process plugin)
    participant APIKeyInj as apikey-injection<br/>(in-process plugin)
    participant NeMoReq as nemo-request-guard<br/>(in-process plugin)
    participant NeMo as NeMo Guardrails<br/>HTTP
    participant Provider as External LLM Provider<br/>(via ServiceEntry)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS SIMPLE

    Note over Client,Provider: Flow 1: External Model Inference Request

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (platform)

    Gateway->>ExtProc: Request Processing<br/>gRPC/9004, Istio mTLS

    ExtProc->>MPR: Process Request<br/>(in-process)
    Note right of MPR: Resolves model name →<br/>provider endpoint + credentials<br/>via CRD in-memory store

    MPR-->>ExtProc: CycleState: provider, endpoint,<br/>auth type, credentials ref

    opt NeMo Guardrails Enabled
        ExtProc->>NeMoReq: Evaluate Input Rails<br/>(in-process)
        NeMoReq->>NeMo: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>HTTP, Configurable
        NeMo-->>NeMoReq: {status: passed/blocked}
        Note right of NeMoReq: If blocked → 403 Forbidden
    end

    ExtProc->>APITrans: Translate Request<br/>(in-process)
    Note right of APITrans: Translates body:<br/>OpenAI → Anthropic/Azure/<br/>Bedrock/Vertex format

    ExtProc->>APIKeyInj: Inject Auth<br/>(in-process)
    Note right of APIKeyInj: Injects provider credentials:<br/>Bearer Token / SigV4 /<br/>API Key header

    ExtProc-->>Gateway: Mutated Request Headers + Body

    Gateway->>Provider: Forward Request<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS SIMPLE<br/>via ExternalName Service +<br/>ServiceEntry + DestinationRule<br/>Auth: Provider-specific

    Provider-->>Gateway: Provider Response<br/>HTTPS/443

    Gateway->>ExtProc: Response Processing<br/>gRPC/9004, Istio mTLS

    opt NeMo Guardrails Enabled
        ExtProc->>NeMoReq: Evaluate Output Rails<br/>(in-process)
        NeMoReq->>NeMo: POST /v1/guardrail/checks<br/>HTTP
        NeMo-->>NeMoReq: {status: passed/blocked}
    end

    ExtProc->>APITrans: Translate Response<br/>(in-process)
    Note right of APITrans: Translates body back<br/>to OpenAI format

    ExtProc-->>Gateway: Mutated Response

    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,Provider: Flow 2: ExternalProvider Reconciliation

    participant User as User/Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    User->>K8sAPI: Create ExternalProvider CR<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+

    K8sAPI-->>ExtProc: Watch Event<br/>HTTPS/443, ServiceAccount Token
    Note right of ExtProc: external-provider-controller

    ExtProc->>K8sAPI: Get Secret (credentials)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    ExtProc->>K8sAPI: Create ExternalName Service<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    ExtProc->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceEntry<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    ExtProc->>K8sAPI: Create DestinationRule<br/>(TLS SIMPLE)<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
    ExtProc->>K8sAPI: Update ExternalProvider Status<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token
